  "industry_note": "Cordierite (2MgO·2Al₂O₃·5SiO₂, orthorhombic Cccm) — **lowest CTE silicate ceramic** (1.5-2.5×10⁻⁶/K — Zerodur 의 5×). Tm 1450°C, ρ 2.65 g/cc, σf 70-130, E 70 GPa, KIC 1.5. Tmax 1400°C continuous. **자동차 catalytic converter substrate** (가장 흔한 — NGK / Corning Celcor honeycomb 표준) — exhaust 800°C cycle thermal shock 견딤. Refractory kiln furniture, glass-melting tool, electric stove burner."
